<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2014-08-27</DATELINE><TITLE>Investigating a Mystery Disease: Tales from a Viral Detective</TITLE><BODY>Viral outbreak investigation is challenging logistically as well as scientifically. In the context of addressing a fictional emerging viral disease, I describe the process of discovery, from the initial report of a problem through discussions of intellectual property and sample management, study design, management, experimental execution, and reporting of results.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>